<h1 class="team-member--name">Mark Fisher</h1>
<div class="team-member--sub-info">
<p>Functions as a Service tech lead, Spring Integration founder</p>
<p>Cambridge, MA</p>
</div>
<div class="team-member--bio">Mark has been a member of the Spring team for over a decade, contributing to the Spring Framework and several other projects. He founded Spring Integration in 2007 and is one of the authors of Spring Integration in Action, published by Manning in 2012. He contributes to Spring Cloud Stream, Spring Cloud Data Flow and Spring Cloud Function and is currently focused on Serverless and Functions as a Service.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
